Revision of the Palaearctic and Oriental species of the genus Naarda Walker, 1866 (Lepidoptera, Erebidae, Hypeninae). Part 3. Description of three new species from AsiaAbstract We revise the Naarda egrettoides species-group and describe and illustrate three new Naarda species: Naarda ardeola sp. n. (Thailand), Naarda egrettoides sp. n. (Thailand) and Naarda pocstamasi sp. n. (Vietnam).